name: The Poet, Jatta Eye
description:
A 1/3 piece from the upcoming sci-fi fantasy Graphic Novel series, veil of the gods - coming soon. This is one of the characters from the series. 

The Poet, Jatta Eye, is an involuntary trans-dimensional traveller, who has managed to make 
his presence felt across almost every permutation of the multi-layered Reality Mesh. 
Dissatisfaction with his chaotic life has led him to formulate a desperate plan. And in the 
process he’s discovered a terrible secret- a secret that will shake the foundations of the 
multiple realities to the core.
